org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.server.jobtracker

Interface JTConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MRConfig

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
@InterfaceStability.Evolving
public interface JTConfig
extends MRConfig
    Place holder for JobTracker server-level configuration. The keys should have "mapreduce.jobtracker." as the prefix
